Janet Waldo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Janet_Waldo 0 Janet Marie Waldo (February 4, 1919 – June 12, 2016) was an American radio and voice actress. She is best known in animation for voicing Judy Jetson, Nancy in Shazzan, Penelope Pitstop, and Josie in Josie and the Pussycats, and on radio as the title character in Meet Corliss Archer.
